* &quot;Missa Sanctae Mariae Magdalenae&quot; (1979) by William Lloyd Webber
* &quot;Mass of Creation&quot; (1984) by Marty Haugen
* &quot;Missa supra Parsifal&quot; (1985) by Dimitri Aguero
